Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.82,0:01:38.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Momma!  Momma!  They chose me!\NI’m an elite pilot!  I’ll defend\Nmankind!  I’m the best in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.90,0:01:43.50,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I have to keep it a secret, so I’ll\Ntell only you, Momma!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:48.51,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Everybody is being so nice to me\Nnow, I won’t feel so lonely anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.54,0:01:53.15,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m okay now, even without Papa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.08,0:01:56.39,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,So, look!  Look at me!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.15,0:01:58.65,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Momma!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.96,0:02:13.97,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Synch ratio zero.  I can’t be the\NSecond Child anymore.  I have\Nno reason left to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.63,0:02:16.87,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Nobody cares about me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.87,0:02:19.30,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,My papa, my momma, nobody cares.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.30,0:02:21.71,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I have no reason left to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.11,0:02:32.65,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are you Asuka Langley Soryu?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.18,0:02:38.15,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Second Intelligence Division\Nreports that they have taken the\NSecond Child into custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.15,0:02:43.19,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Really?  It isn’t like them to lose her\Nin the first place and then to take\Nseven days to find her.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.19,0:02:47.73,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,They must have done so intentionally.\NThey’re trying to make trouble\Nfor us, aren’t they?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.73,0:02:49.23,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,They could be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.60,0:02:55.08,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}The Fifth Child arrives to replace\NAsuka today.  This whole thing\Nis just too convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.01,0:03:04.98,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Rei Ayanami...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.98,0:03:06.52,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,There’s a feeling about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.52,0:03:08.83,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Almost like...  my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.89,0:03:12.70,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Rei Ayanami...  and my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.46,0:03:16.03,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What are you doing with\Nthem, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:19.60,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Commander Ikari...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.26,0:03:24.27,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Did you know my cat died?  The cat\Nmy grandmother was taking care of?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.87,0:03:30.15,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I hadn’t taken care of it for a long\Ntime, but now I know that I’ll\Nnever see it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.34,0:03:34.12,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Why did you destroy\Nthe dummy system?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.61,0:03:38.25,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It wasn’t the dummy system that I\Ndestroyed.  It was Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.31,0:03:42.18,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’ll ask you once more.\NWhy did you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.18,0:03:45.35,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m not happy anymore, not even\Nwhen you make love to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.35,0:03:48.86,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Go ahead and do whatever you want\Nwith my body, it’s never\Nstopped you before!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.86,0:03:50.79,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You disappoint me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.79,0:03:52.09,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Disappoint?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.09,0:03:54.90,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You had no hopes or expectations\Nof me to start with!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.90,0:03:58.28,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I was nothing!  I am nothing!!\NNothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.27,0:04:04.68,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What can I do now, Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.64,0:04:09.35,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Asuka, where have you\Ndisappeared to?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.41,0:04:15.06,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}But what could I talk to her about?\NCould I talk about Ayanami\Nwith her?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.69,0:04:28.14,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In,{\fad(170,0)}Toji, Kensuke...  Their homes were\Ndestroyed and now they’ve left.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.30,0:04:33.77,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Friends...  I don’t have anybody left\Nwhom I could call my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:36.11,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Nobody!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.71,0:04:39.88,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I can’t go see Ayanami again.  I don’t\Nhave the courage to face her.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:42.64,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t even know how to talk or\Nact around her now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.05,0:04:49.43,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade Out,{\fad(0,170)}Asuka...  Misato...  Mother...\NWhat do I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.92,0:04:51.42,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.04,0:05:13.54,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Singing is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:18.58,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Singing brings joy and revitalizes the\Nsoul.  I think that song is the greatest\Nachievement of Lilim culture.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.65,0:05:21.15,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t you agree...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:24.15,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...Shinji Ikari?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:25.32,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.32,0:05:27.19,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Everyone knows your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.19,0:05:31.39,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t mean to sound rude,\Nbut you’re rather ignorant\Nof your own position.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.39,0:05:34.90,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Really?  And you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.90,0:05:39.73,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I am Kaoru, Kaoru Nagisa.  I’m like\Nyou, one of the selected children...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.73,0:05:41.27,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...the Fifth Child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.27,0:05:43.68,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re the Fifth Child?!  You...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.54,0:05:45.44,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Mister Nagisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:47.78,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Call me Kaoru, Mister Ikari.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.78,0:05:50.55,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh no, you can call me Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.42,0:05:56.95,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Fifth Child has just arrived.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.55,0:06:02.42,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Kaoru Nagisa, Kaoru of the\NSeashore.  And all of his records\Nhave been erased, just like Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.42,0:06:06.23,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But one record remains.\NHe was born on the day\NSecond Impact occurred.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.23,0:06:10.73,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The committee sent him directly to\Nus.  There must be something else.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:14.47,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Marduk Report’s file on the\NFifth Child was classified...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.47,0:06:18.31,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...so I hacked into the Intelligence\NDepartment’s computer system.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.31,0:06:20.24,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I can’t believe you did that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.24,0:06:21.92,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It was worth doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.91,0:06:24.58,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I found out where Ritsuko is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.81,0:06:27.82,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What do you want to do about the\NFifth Child’s synch tests?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.82,0:06:33.09,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t have any tricks up my sleeve\Nthis time.  Let’s see what he can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.79,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Down another 0.3.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.79,0:06:38.29,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.46,0:06:41.46,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are these data readouts correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.46,0:06:44.50,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,All testing systems are\Noperating correctly, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.50,0:06:47.44,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The MAGI confirm that there\Nare no data errors.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.44,0:06:52.47,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s incredible that he can synch\Nwith Unit 02 before we’ve even\Nconfigured the core.  He’s amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.47,0:06:54.48,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But this isn’t possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.48,0:06:57.18,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,On this system it can’t happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.18,0:06:58.95,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Nevertheless, it is happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.95,0:07:02.45,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,We must accept that fact and start\Nan investigation into why\Nit’s happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.12,0:07:10.03,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re the First Child, aren’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.69,0:07:13.20,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Rei Ayanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.23,0:07:16.04,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re the same as I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.73,0:07:18.23,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.80,0:07:21.84,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Fifth Child has made\Ncontact with Rei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.84,0:07:23.04,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:26.61,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The MAGI are currently analyzing the\Nnature of the Fifth and what\Nhis powers may be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.61,0:07:29.98,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In,{\fad(170,0)}We still don’t know who\Nor what he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.98,0:07:32.13,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade Out,{\fad(0,170)}Who in the hell is this boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:42.10,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji hasn’t come back yet either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.66,0:07:44.76,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m not deserving of his trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.13,0:07:51.87,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Central Dogma is now open.\NPlease use Route 3 to transfer.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:54.18,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hi, you weren’t waiting here\Nfor me, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.90,0:07:57.91,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, well, not really waiting anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.91,0:07:59.24,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,So what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.24,0:08:04.21,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, usually when the tests are\Nover, I’ll just take a shower\Nand go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.38,0:08:09.05,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But I don’t really want to\Ngo home these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.05,0:08:14.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The fact that you have a place where\Nyou can return, a home, will lead\Nyou to happiness.  That’s good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.56,0:08:15.79,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.79,0:08:19.47,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’d like to talk some more.\NMay I come with you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.70,0:08:22.97,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,To the shower.\NAren’t you going now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.60,0:08:25.63,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Or do you mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:28.41,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Oh, no, I don’t mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.31,0:08:38.42,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You are extremely afraid\Nof first contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.21,0:08:41.13,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Are you that scared of affection?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.98,0:08:46.79,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,If you don’t get close to others,\Nyou won’t be betrayed and\Nyou won’t hurt each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.79,0:08:49.79,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,However, neither will you\Nforget what loneliness is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:56.06,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Man can never make loneliness\Ndisappear because man is alone,\Nbut man can forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.06,0:08:59.24,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,So, man can find the will to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.11,0:09:08.51,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s time.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.51,0:09:10.08,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is this it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:12.45,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I have to go to bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.45,0:09:13.15,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,With me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:17.90,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, you have your own\Nroom, I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:20.42,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.02,0:09:24.09,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Man always has pain in his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.53,0:09:29.00,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Since his heart feels pain,\Nhe experiences life as pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:34.00,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You are delicate like glass.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.00,0:09:34.80,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.80,0:09:37.44,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, and that earns my sympathy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.44,0:09:38.87,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Sympathy?
Dialogue: 3,0:09:38.87,0:09:40.38,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Text,In other words, I like you.
