Dialogue: 2,0:09:42.71,0:09:46.52,Title (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Video Text,{\c&H000000&}{\blur0.7}{\pos(320,237)}The Last Angel
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.22,0:09:54.79,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,NERV was formed as SEELE’s\Nexecutive branch.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.79,0:09:58.59,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It was created to carry\Nout our scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.59,0:10:02.40,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,However, it has been taken\Nover by a selfish man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.40,0:10:05.40,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, it has.  We must return\Nit to our control.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.40,0:10:07.27,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Before the promised day.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.27,0:10:11.01,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,We must restore NERV and the Eva\Nseries to their original purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:15.15,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ikari will answer to SEELE\Nfor his malfeasance.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.91,0:10:18.95,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It will not be much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:23.86,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Lance of Longinus that was\Nhindering our wish is gone forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.69,0:10:29.32,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The last Angel should appear soon\Nand our wish will be attained upon\Ndestroying that Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.32,0:10:31.50,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Soon, very soon, Yui.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.92,0:10:35.61,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.13,0:10:39.04,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}Why am I still alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.53,0:10:41.37,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}For what purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.77,0:10:43.61,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}For whose purpose?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.00,0:10:45.64,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}The Fifth Child...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.64,0:10:49.24,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}In what way are he and I alike?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.24,0:10:50.79,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.72,0:11:01.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I am glad this apartment is in the\Nsuburbs.  Thank God you were safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.22,0:11:04.50,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But there is no guarantee\Nthis won’t happen again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:08.63,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,So, the Horaki family will take care\Nof you starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.63,0:11:11.11,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I won’t be able to see you\Nfor a while, Pen Pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.67,0:11:21.11,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I think I should sleep on the floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.11,0:11:25.15,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, I am staying at your place.\NI should sleep down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.58,0:11:31.76,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What do you want to talk about?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.95,0:11:35.49,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You want me to listen to\Nyou, don’t you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.06,0:11:39.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Many things have happened since\NI came here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.83,0:11:46.37,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I used to live with my teacher.\NThey were calm and boring days.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.17,0:11:48.88,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I was just living...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.74,0:11:52.14,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But I was fine with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:54.28,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,There was really nothing I had to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.94,0:11:56.78,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Do you hate people?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:12:00.08,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Not really, I don’t care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:02.43,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,But I hate my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.92,0:12:06.79,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}Why did I tell Kaoru that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.99,0:12:12.80,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I was probably born to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:17.40,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Did you get his data?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.40,0:12:20.84,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is it.  I got this from Ibuki\Nwithout her knowledge.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.84,0:12:24.15,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m sorry that I made you do this.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.17,0:12:26.07,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.07,0:12:30.21,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No wonder Maya can’t reveal this.\NThis is not theoretically possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.21,0:12:33.68,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You’re right.  The issue gets\Neven more mysterious.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.68,0:12:38.60,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,How can he fix the synch ratio at\Nwhatever point he wishes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.19,0:12:41.57,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I have to take another chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.96,0:12:44.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What a surprise to see you here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.53,0:12:46.46,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I have a question for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.46,0:12:48.66,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Our conversation is monitored here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:50.10,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t care.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.10,0:12:53.24,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What is the boy, the Fifth Child?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.17,0:12:56.17,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,He is probably the last Angel.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.61,0:13:02.75,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Well, let’s go.  Come, Adam’s alter\Nego and Lilith’s minion.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.05,0:13:11.52,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Eva Unit 02 is activating!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.59,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That’s impossible!  Where’s Asuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.59,0:13:16.29,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,She’s in room 303!\NI’ve just confirmed it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.29,0:13:17.73,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Then who the hell is piloting it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.73,0:13:21.26,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It is unmanned!  There is no entry\Nplug inserted in Unit 02!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.26,0:13:24.55,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}Unmanned?  So, the Fifth\NChild is not there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:28.34,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,AT Field detected in\NCentral Dogma!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.34,0:13:29.10,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is it Unit 02?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.10,0:13:32.27,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, the blood pattern is blue!\NIt’s definitely an Angel!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.27,0:13:33.78,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What the hell?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.71,0:13:36.75,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That boy?  An Angel?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.85,0:13:41.68,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Target has passed the Fourth Layer\Nand is still descending.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.68,0:13:43.89,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s no good!  We can’t cut the\Npower to the linear carriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:45.49,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Target has passed the Fifth Layer.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:50.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Close all Central Dogma shutters!\NBuy us some time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.43,0:13:55.97,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Closing all shutters immediately.\NAll personnel evacuate.\NAll personnel evacuate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:14:00.23,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Unbelievable, SEELE itself\Nsent an Angel to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.23,0:14:04.15,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The old men want to advance\Nanother step with our help.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.77,0:14:09.34,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The last Angel has invaded Central\NDogma.  It is currently descending.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.34,0:14:10.61,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Just as we planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.61,0:14:17.45,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Ikari, you were our good friend,\Nour comrade and conspirator,\Nbut this is your last job.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.45,0:14:21.53,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I expect that you will use Unit 01\Nto accomplish the mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.03,0:14:26.99,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Unit 02 has penetrated\Nthe armored shutters!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.99,0:14:29.26,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Target has passed the second wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.26,0:14:31.33,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Pursue it with Unit 01.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.33,0:14:32.17,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.17,0:14:36.81,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Use any means to keep it from\Ninvading Terminal Dogma.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.74,0:14:42.51,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}But why did the Angel take Unit 02?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.51,0:14:45.45,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Is it going to fuse with Unit 02?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.45,0:14:48.05,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Or is it going to bring destruction?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.05,0:14:54.19,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Lie!  Lie!  It’s a lie!!  I don’t believe\Nthat Kaoru is an Angel!  It’s a lie!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.19,0:14:57.43,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is a fact, face it.  Sortie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.43,0:14:58.93,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.00,0:15:03.74,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Shinji is late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.37,0:15:08.04,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Eva Unit 01 is descending via\NRoute 2.  Pursuing the target.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.04,0:15:11.51,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You betrayed me!\NYou hurt my feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:13.71,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You betrayed me just like\Nmy father did!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.71,0:15:17.25,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Unit 01 has reached the Fourth\NLayer.  It’s about to confront\Nthe target!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.25,0:15:18.75,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.28,0:15:21.35,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I have been waiting for you, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.35,0:15:22.85,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.26,0:15:29.13,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m sorry, Asuka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.89,0:15:36.73,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Eva series were born from\NAdam.  The entire human race\Nmust abhor their existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.73,0:15:39.67,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Lilim try to survive even if it\Nmeans taking advantage of\Nthe thing they hate.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.67,0:15:41.20,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I do not understand this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:47.14,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Kaoru, stop this!\NWhy are you doing this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.14,0:15:50.04,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Eva is created from the\Nsame tissue as I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.04,0:15:52.65,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I am also born from Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.65,0:15:55.25,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,So I can synchronize with it as\Neasily as if it had no soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.25,0:15:58.99,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Unit 02’s soul is now\Nshutting itself up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:02.42,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,An AT Field?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.42,0:16:05.66,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Yes, that’s what you\NLilim call this.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.66,0:16:09.87,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is the light of the soul,\Nsacred territory where no\None should intrude.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.53,0:16:12.60,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Don’t you Lilim know?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.60,0:16:16.20,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Everybody has an AT Field.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.20,0:16:18.48,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t understand what\Nyou’re talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.24,0:16:22.84,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Both Evas have reached\Nthe deepest layer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.84,0:16:25.29,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Target is 20 meters away from\NTerminal Dogma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.75,0:16:30.38,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,If Unit 01’s signal disappears and\Nthen any change occurs...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:33.99,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I know; self-destruct\Nthe entire complex.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.99,0:16:36.92,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s better than letting the\NThird Impact occur.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.92,0:16:38.33,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I’m sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.33,0:16:41.23,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t mind it if it’s with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.23,0:16:42.73,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.73,0:16:51.71,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,Fade In & Out,{\fad(170,170)}It is human fate.  Human hope\Nis made with sorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.88,0:16:55.84,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.84,0:16:58.68,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The strongest AT Field ever\Nhas been detected!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.68,0:17:03.02,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s shutting out everything!  Light,\Nmagnetism, sub-atomic particles!\NWe can’t monitor anything!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.02,0:17:04.45,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,This is absolutely impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.45,0:17:09.47,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Signals from the target, Unit 02\Nand Unit 01 are lost!  We’ve lost\Ncommunication with the pilot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.54,0:17:23.04,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Kaoru!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:27.71,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Wait!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:40.79,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Final safety system released!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:42.96,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Heaven’s Door is opening!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.23,0:17:46.71,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,The Angel has finally reached it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:49.00,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Hyuga...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.60,0:17:55.34,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.34,0:17:56.30,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What’s going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.30,0:17:57.61,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Another AT Field!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.61,0:18:01.71,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,A field as strong as the first one has\Nappeared around Terminal Dogma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.38,0:18:04.48,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,It’s invading the other AT Field!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.48,0:18:06.41,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Impossible!  Is it another Angel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:08.02,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t know!  I can’t confirm it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.02,0:18:10.65,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,God!  It just disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.65,0:18:12.46,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Disappeared?  The Angel has?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.72,0:18:16.09,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Adam...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.09,0:18:21.66,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,...our mother.  One who is born from\NAdam must return to Adam.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.66,0:18:23.37,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Although it could destroy\Nall humanity?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.00,0:18:28.50,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No!  This is...  Lilith?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.50,0:18:30.81,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I see.  I understand Lilim.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.59,0:18:46.52,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Thank you, Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.52,0:18:49.56,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I wanted you to stop Unit 02.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.56,0:18:52.93,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Otherwise I would survive with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.93,0:18:55.13,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Kaoru, why?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.13,0:19:00.43,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Because it is my destiny to live\Nalthough it would bring\Ndestruction to humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.60,0:19:06.67,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I would prefer to die here.  Life\Nand death are equal to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.67,0:19:10.28,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Death of the self, that is the\Nonly absolute freedom.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.28,0:19:11.31,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,What are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.95,0:19:16.29,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I don’t understand what\Nyou’re talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.85,0:19:18.13,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,That is my will.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.05,0:19:20.93,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Now, destroy me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.02,0:19:24.59,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Otherwise you will be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.16,0:19:30.33,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Only one life form can be chosen to\Nevade the destruction and\Ninherit the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.33,0:19:33.34,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,And you are not the existence\Nthat should die.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.17,0:19:41.59,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You need the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.34,0:19:46.92,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Thank you, my life was meaningful\Nbecause of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.43,0:21:15.71,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Kaoru said he liked me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.24,0:21:23.55,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I have never...  never had\Nsuch kind words.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.48,0:21:28.62,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,He was like me, and like Ayanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.89,0:21:32.26,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,I liked him, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.55,0:21:41.03,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Kaoru should have survived.\NHe was much better than I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:45.50,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,Kaoru should have survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:49.47,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,No, the one who survives is the one\Nwho has the will to survive.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.60,0:21:56.18,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,He wished for death.  He neglected\Nhis will to survive and chose\Na false hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.18,0:21:58.12,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,You are not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.88,0:22:02.09,ADV VHS (640 x 480),,0,0,0,,How can you be so cruel?
